<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
MEDICAL SUPPLIES (MDS)
</IN>
<LP>
   ROCHESTER, N.Y. -- Eastman Kodak Co. has taken an equity
position in Vortech Data Inc., a Reston, Va., supplier of
medical-image management systems. Terms weren't disclosed.
   The two companies are establishing an alliance that will
include a joint product development and marketing program.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Eastman Kodak is a leading supplier of medical diagnostic
imaging systems, including electronic products and X-ray
film.
